      "text": "%md\n---\n### Cell 6: Kiem tra Label va Model truoc khi train\nChay thu 1 batch nho (30 step) de xac nhan model va data tuong thich.\nNeu Acc > 50% -> PASS. San sang train chinh thuc.",
